aConditionPackages=&lt;packages&gt;<br/>task exit code is informational only]\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:197:  nativeTraceImage`, `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage`, and `./gradlew\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:202:  `-PmetadataConfigDirs=run-0,run-1,...`. The Gradle task is responsible\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:270:    (`nativeTraceImage`, `runNativeTraceImage`, or\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:296:### 7.1 `nativeTraceImage`\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:304:| `-PmetadataConfigDirs=<dir1,dir2,...>` | no | Comma-separated absolute paths translated to `-H:ConfigurationFileDirectories=...`. Omitted on the first iteration. |\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:316:### 7.2 `runNativeTraceImage`\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:318:Runs the binary produced by `nativeTraceImage` once, capturing traced\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:327:| `-PtraceMetadataPath=<absolute path>` | yes | Becomes `-XX:TraceMetadata=path=...`. Must be a fresh per-iteration directory. |\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:329:| `-PmetadataConfigDirs=<dir1,dir2,...>` | no | Comma-separated absolute paths of prior accepted trace dirs; translated to `-H:ConfigurationFileDirectories=...` so the rebuild sees what tracing has already collected. Omitted on the first iteration. |\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:339:  the metadata supplied via `-PmetadataConfigDirs`, instead of throwing.\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:353:  exhaustion, or a `nativeTraceImage` build failure — never on the run\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:517:   nativeTraceImage`, passing all prior raw `metadata-run-<i>` directories\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:518:   as `-PmetadataConfigDirs=run-0,run-1,...` from the second iteration\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:519:   onward. The first iteration omits `-PmetadataConfigDirs`.\n./forge/docs/nativ